Class XmlStackFrame

Provides stack trace information about an executing query to the methods of XmlDebugListener.

Remarks

XmlStackFrame objects describe a stack frame in the stack trace and includes a pointer to the previous stack frame.

Query(String)

System.String queryString

Returns
Type Description
XmlResults

A XmlResults object containing query results.
Remarks

This can be used to examine the value of the context item (".") or variables ("$var") for a given stack frame as well as other parts of the dynamic context.

caution

Users may find that the context item and variables present in their original query do not exist during query execution due to optimization performed by DB XML.
